On January 28, 2004, C. R. Bard, Inc. issued a press release reporting earnings and other financial results for its fourth quarter and twelve months ended December 31, 2003. A copy of the press release is attached as Exhibit 99.1. The information in this press release is furnished not filed.
Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the Registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned hereunto duly authorized.
