Event Transcript
C. R. Bard, Inc.
Q3 2004 Earnings Conference Call
Event Date/Time: October 19, 2004/5:00 p.m.
Event Duration: 48 minutes
Corporate Participants
Timothy M. Ring
C. R. Bard, Inc. - Chairman and CEO
John H. Weiland
C. R. Bard, Inc. - President and COO
Todd C. Schermerhorn
