(a) . Each of the Borrower and its Subsidiaries has good title to, or valid leasehold interests in, all its real and personal property material to its business, subject only to Liens permitted by Section 6.01 and except where the defects in title or in the validity of any interests in such real or personal property could not, individually or in the aggregate, reasonably be expected to result in a Material Adverse Effect.
