The following information is being furnished pursuant to Item 2.02.
On July 22, 2010, C. R. Bard, Inc. issued a press release reporting earnings and other financial results for the second quarter ended June 30, 2010. A copy of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated by reference in this Item 2.02. The information in this press release shall not be treated as filed for purposes of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended.
 
