"" means an arrangement with any person providing for the leasing by C. R. Bard, Inc. or a Subsidiary of any Restricted Property whereby such Restricted Property has been or is to be sold or transferred by C. R. Bard, Inc. or a Subsidiary to such person other than C. R. Bard, Inc. or any Subsidiary; provided, however, that the foregoing shall not apply to any such arrangement involving a lease for a term, including extension or renewal rights, for not more than three years.
